      <h1>Lucerne Grand: Is the Lakeside Mega-Launch the Crown Jewel of the West?</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="post-content">
    <figure class="post-cover" style="margin:0;">
      <img src="/assets/images/lucerne-grand-cover.jpg" alt="Lucerne Grand — CDL's ~575-unit OCR launch on Lakeside Drive, with 1-minute walks to both Lakeside MRT and Jurong Lake Gardens" loading="eager" decoding="async" />
